`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- **Seamless terrain**: All chunks must use the **same** SeededNoise seed with **global** world-space coordinates — not per-chunk seeds. This matches the spec ("terrain noise and biome blending use global coordinates") and prevents visible seams at chunk boundaries.
- **Tests use real Miniplex world**: Following the ZoneLoader.test.ts pattern — no mocking, cleanup via `afterEach(() => world.remove(...))`. This catches real ECS entity lifecycle bugs.
- **Pure function extraction**: `worldToChunkCoords`, `getChunksInRadius`, `getChunkKey` are standalone exports so they can be unit-tested without setting up a ChunkManager instance.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
